---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import site from '../data/site.json';
---

<BaseLayout title={`About — ${site.title}`} description="Fullstack Software Engineer specializing in Laravel SaaS architecture, payment gateways, and multi-tenant systems.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="animate-fade-in-up mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-text dark:text-white sm:text-4xl">
        <span data-i18n-id>Tentang Saya</span><span data-i18n-en>About Me</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-text-muted dark:text-slate-400">
        <span data-i18n-id>Software Engineer dengan 6+ tahun pengalaman membangun sistem SaaS multi-tenant.</span>
        <span data-i18n-en>Software Engineer with 6+ years of experience building multi-tenant SaaS systems.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-text-muted dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed scroll-reveal">
      <p>
        <span data-i18n-id>Hai! Saya <strong class="text-text dark:text-slate-200">{site.author}</strong>, Fullstack Software Engineer yang berspesialisasi dalam arsitektur SaaS berbasis Laravel. Saya memiliki pengalaman 6+ tahun merancang dan membangun sistem multi-tenant, payment gateway, serta platform bisnis yang terintegrasi dengan infrastruktur jaringan (Mikrotik API).</span>
        <span data-i18n-en>Hi! I'm <strong class="text-text dark:text-slate-200">{site.author}</strong>, a Fullstack Software Engineer specializing in Laravel-based SaaS architecture. I have 6+ years of experience designing and building multi-tenant systems, payment gateways, and business platforms integrated with network infrastructure (Mikrotik API).</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        <span data-i18n-id>Saya telah mengembangkan 34+ proyek profesional mulai dari sistem POS, payment hub, WMS, HRIS, hingga aplikasi cross-platform. Fokus utama saya adalah membangun sistem yang skalabel, aman, dan mudah dipelihara untuk kebutuhan bisnis nyata.</span>
        <span data-i18n-en>I've developed 34+ professional projects ranging from POS systems, payment hubs, WMS, HRIS, to cross-platform applications. My primary focus is building scalable, secure, and maintainable systems for real business needs.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Skills -->
    <div class="mt-16 scroll-reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.1s">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text dark:text-white">
        <span data-i18n-id>Keahlian & Teknologi</span><span data-i18n-en>Skills & Technologies</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
        <!-- Backend -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-accent mb-2">Backend</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {['PHP', 'Laravel', 'MySQL', 'REST API', 'Livewire', 'Queue/Jobs'].map((skill) => (
              <span class="rounded-full border border-border dark:border-slate-600 bg-surface dark:bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-text dark:text-slate-200">
                {skill}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Frontend -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-accent mb-2">Frontend</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {['JavaScript', 'TypeScript', 'Tailwind CSS', 'Bootstrap', 'Alpine.js', 'Blade'].map((skill) => (
              <span class="rounded-full border border-border dark:border-slate-600 bg-surface dark:bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-text dark:text-slate-200">
                {skill}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Cross-Platform & Desktop -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-accent mb-2">Cross-Platform & Desktop</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {['ElectronJS', 'Flutter', 'Ionic', 'Dart', 'Angular'].map((skill) => (
              <span class="rounded-full border border-border dark:border-slate-600 bg-surface dark:bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-text dark:text-slate-200">
                {skill}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Integrations & Infrastructure -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-accent mb-2">
            <span data-i18n-id>Integrasi & Infrastruktur</span><span data-i18n-en>Integrations & Infrastructure</span>
          </h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {['Mikrotik API', 'Tripay', 'QRIS', 'Midtrans', 'Git', 'Linux', 'Docker', 'Nginx'].map((skill) => (
              <span class="rounded-full border border-border dark:border-slate-600 bg-surface dark:bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-text dark:text-slate-200">
                {skill}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- What I Do -->
    <div class="mt-16 scroll-reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.2s">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text dark:text-white">
        <span data-i18n-id>Spesialisasi</span><span data-i18n-en>Specializations</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-4 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-slate-200">
            <span data-i18n-id>Arsitektur SaaS Multi-Tenant</span><span data-i18n-en>Multi-Tenant SaaS Architecture</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-slate-400">
            <span data-i18n-id>Merancang sistem SaaS dengan isolasi data per tenant, role management, dan skalabilitas horizontal.</span>
            <span data-i18n-en>Designing SaaS systems with per-tenant data isolation, role management, and horizontal scalability.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-slate-200">
            <span data-i18n-id>Integrasi Payment Gateway</span><span data-i18n-en>Payment Gateway Integration</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-slate-400">
            <span data-i18n-id>Membangun sistem pembayaran terintegrasi Tripay, QRIS, dan Midtrans dengan auto-reconciliation.</span>
            <span data-i18n-en>Building payment systems integrated with Tripay, QRIS, and Midtrans with auto-reconciliation.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-slate-200">
            <span data-i18n-id>Sistem Berbasis Jaringan</span><span data-i18n-en>Network-Connected Systems</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-slate-400">
            <span data-i18n-id>Platform ISP, voucher WiFi hotspot, dan manajemen bandwidth terintegrasi Mikrotik API.</span>
            <span data-i18n-en>ISP platforms, WiFi hotspot vouchers, and bandwidth management integrated with Mikrotik API.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-slate-200">
            <span data-i18n-id>Aplikasi Desktop & Mobile</span><span data-i18n-en>Desktop & Mobile Apps</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-slate-400">
            <span data-i18n-id>Aplikasi desktop dengan ElectronJS dan mobile cross-platform menggunakan Flutter & Ionic.</span>
            <span data-i18n-en>Desktop applications with ElectronJS and cross-platform mobile apps using Flutter & Ionic.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Certifications -->
    <div class="mt-16 scroll-reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.3s">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text dark:text-white">
        <span data-i18n-id>Sertifikasi & Pelatihan</span><span data-i18n-en>Certifications & Training</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
        {[
          { name: 'Learn the Fundamental Steps to Become a Web Programmer', org: 'Hacktiv8', year: '2022' },
          { name: 'HTML Course', org: 'Sololearn', year: '2022' },
          { name: 'PHP Course', org: 'Sololearn', year: '2022' },
          { name: 'Python for Beginners', org: 'Sololearn', year: '2022' },
          { name: 'Python (Basic) Certificate', org: 'HackerRank', year: '2022' },
          { name: 'BAPAREKRAF Developer Day 2022', org: 'Kemenparekraf RI', year: '2022' },
          { name: 'Laravel Web Programming', org: 'Camp404', year: '2021' },
          { name: 'Junior Web Programmer', org: 'Badan Nasional Sertifikasi Profesi (BNSP)', year: '2021' },
          { name: 'BAPAREKRAF Developer Day 2020', org: 'Kemenparekraf RI', year: '2020' },
          { name: 'NDG Linux Essentials', org: 'Cisco Networking Academy', year: '2018' },
          { name: 'CCNA Routing and Switching', org: 'Cisco Networking Academy', year: '2018' },
        ].map((cert) => (
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 rounded-lg border border-border dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 transition-all hover:shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10 text-primary">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-slate-200 text-sm">{cert.name}</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-text-muted dark:text-slate-400">{cert.org} · {cert.year}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
